# 创建环境变量模板
New-Item -Path .env.example -ItemType File
```

**编辑 `.env.example`**：
```
# OpenAI API Key
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here

# Clerk Authentication
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=your-clerk-secret-key-here
CLERK_JWKS_URL=your-clerk-jwks-url-here
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=your-clerk-publishable-key-here

# FDA API Key (Optional)
FDA_API_KEY=your-fda-api-key-here

# PubMed API
PUBMED_API_KEY=your-pubmed-api-key-here
NCBI_EMAIL=your-email@example.com

# AWS Configuration (if deploying to AWS)
AWS_ACCOUNT_ID=your-aws-account-id
DEFAULT_AWS_REGION=us-east-1